      "id": "https://uofa.net/synth/validation/morrison-cpb-rhi-comparison-2025",
      "type": "ValidationResult",
      "name": "Relative hemolysis index validation against FDA generic pump experimental data",
      "description": "CFD-predicted RHI values compared against published FDA generic centrifugal pump experimental hemolysis measurements (Herbertson et al. 2015; FDA 2017 benchmark dataset). Mean RHI prediction error across 5 operating points: 8.3%. All predicted RHI values satisfy RH < 1 acceptance criterion relative to predicate device. Validation conducted using 2025-Q3 model platform with revised impeller clearance geometry."
    },
    {
      "id": "https://uofa.net/synth/validation/morrison-cpb-mesh-convergence-2025",
      "type": "ValidationResult",
      "name": "Mesh convergence study — 3-level Richardson extrapolation",
      "description": "Three mesh refinement levels (coarse: 4.2M cells, medium: 11.7M cells, fine: 28.4M cells) evaluated using Richardson extrapolation. Grid convergence index (GCI) for shear stress scalar field: 2.1% (fine-to-medium). Discretization error contribution to RHI QoI bounded at 3.4%. Convergence monotonic across all operating points."
    },
    {
      "id": "https://uofa.net/synth/validation/morrison-cpb-solver-verification-2025",
      "type": "ValidationResult",
      "name": "Numerical solver verification — manufactured solution benchmark",
      "description": "ANSYS Fluent 2024 R2 verified against method-of-manufactured-solutions benchmark for rotating frame Navier-Stokes. Second-order spatial convergence confirmed. Residual convergence criterion 1e-6 applied uniformly. Software version control log maintained under QMS document QMS-SW-2024-112."
    }
  ],
