      "rationale": "Three-level mesh convergence study performed. GCI for shear stress scalar field 2.1% (fine-to-medium transition). Discretization error contribution to RHI bounded at 3.4%, within acceptable range for MRL 2. Monotonic convergence confirmed across all 5 operating points. Discretization error level 2 achieved."
    },
    {
      "factorStandard": "ASME-VV40-2018",
      "factorType": "Test conditions",
      "type": "CredibilityFactor",
      "requiredLevel": 2,
      "achievedLevel": 2,
      "factorStatus": "assessed",
      "acceptanceCriteria": "Experimental test conditions used for validation are documented with sufficient fidelity to assess their relevance to the COU operating envelope. Required level 2 per MRL 2.",
      "rationale": "FDA generic pump experimental data (Herbertson et al. 2015) conducted at 37°C, bovine blood at standardized hematocrit 33±2%. Five operating points (2.5 L/min at 2500 RPM through 6.0 L/min at 3500 RPM) span CPB clinical operating envelope. Test conditions documented in FDA benchmark report and independently verified. Level 2 achieved."
    },
