      "acceptanceCriteria": "Numerical solver error beyond discretization (iterative convergence, round-off) documented or shown negligible. Level 1 acceptable at MRL 2 for this factor.",
      "rationale": "Iterative convergence to residual 1e-6 applied uniformly. Round-off error negligible for double-precision arithmetic at operating mesh sizes. Formal quantification not required at MRL 2 level 1; solver error treated as negligible relative to discretization and model form contributions. Not assessed beyond confirmation of convergence criterion."
    },
