      "factorStatus": "not-assessed",
      "acceptanceCriteria": "Errors arising from incorrect application of the simulation tool are addressed at level 1 through analyst qualification records. Level 1 acceptable at MRL 2.",
      "rationale": "Lead analyst holds documented CFD qualification per internal training record TR-2024-CFD-07. Simulation setup reviewed by second analyst prior to production runs. Formal use-error analysis not required at MRL 2 level 1. Not assessed beyond qualification confirmation."
