      "acceptanceCriteria": "Model form assumptions (turbulence model, hemolysis power-law coefficients, blood rheology) documented. Level 1 acceptable at MRL 2 for this factor.",
      "rationale": "SST k-omega turbulence model selected based on published literature for rotating blood-contacting devices. Giersiepen-Wurzinger hemolysis model with standard coefficients (C=3.62e-5, alpha=2.416, beta=0.785) applied. Blood modeled as non-Newtonian Carreau fluid. Model form sensitivity not formally quantified; level 1 documentation of assumptions maintained. Not assessed beyond documentation."
    },
