      "rationale": "FDA generic pump experimental specimens fabricated to published benchmark geometry (FDA 2017). Blood samples: bovine blood sourced per Herbertson et al. 2015 protocol, hematocrit 33±2%, anticoagulated with EDTA. Sample characterization records available in FDA benchmark dataset documentation. Not assessed beyond documentation review."
