    "rationale": "All 7 assessed credibility factors achieve required levels per ASME V&V 40-2018 MRL 2 gradation tables. Six factors documented as not-assessed at level 1, consistent with MRL 2 requirements. RHI validation error of 8.3% mean across operating points is within acceptable range for the COU decision. The model platform (2025-Q3 baseline incorporating DCN-2025-047 impeller geometry update) is considered fit for purpose. Requirement binding to ASME V&V 40-2018 confirmed. Credibility assessment accepted for regulatory submission.",
